<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>SCP-CN-1883</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020/6/3</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lei-height" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6353411); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6353411&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569479" alt="Lei Height" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6353411)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lei-height" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6353411); return false;">Lei Height</a></span></p>
